response.overview: British stockbroker Nicholas Winton visits Czechoslovakia in the 1930s and forms plans to assist in the rescue of Jewish children before the onset of World War II, in an operation that came to be known as the Kindertransport.
response.tagline: Save one life, save the world.
response.title: One Life

titles.title: ONE LIFE 奇跡が繋いだ6000の命

results.name: One Life brings the story of Nicholas Winton's WWII heroics to the BFI London Film Festival
